Transcription.Text: The system which was devised consists of a composite diagram such as that illustrated at Fig. 1. The pecked line on the diagram indicates its method of use. The top lefthand section is entered with the appropriate value of the first predictor and successive turns are made at the appropriate isopleths of each of the other predictors, the forecast being read from the scale exit.
